title: Curtis Woodman Explores & Destroys
description: Description: It's raw, it's self-made, it's snowboarding and Curtis Woodman is exploring and destroying anything and everything he can find in this the lost year of snowboarding. Splitboarding, hiking, finding it and dropping, slashing and tearing it up. Get rattled and get rad.
